{"id":"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07","title":"第 7 課 - 向元件樣板中新增內嵌","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"lesson-7---add-an-interpolation-to-a-components-template\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"18nvspb62rg8jngwgehwv37lr\">第 7 課 - 向元件樣板中新增內嵌<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#lesson-7---add-an-interpolation-to-a-components-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8hj9lvhhteamdza28mz2jjcji\">本教程示範瞭如何向 Angular 樣板中新增內嵌，以便在樣板中顯示動態資料。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9b0304m4wmxslkazn9h6yr4kn\"><strong>預計時間</strong>: 約10分鐘</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"779lizxt04qy27m7ny4sr2bs7\"><strong>起始程式碼:</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-06\"></live-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5wlhomt876f84ne5w3wiwyear\"><strong>完成程式碼:</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-07\"></live-example></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-youll-learn\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy8qhuh22qozu5okjmjfdf3nx\">你將學到<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#what-youll-learn\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckyc75th2r7ddnol8xwkgrc5s\">應用程式將在 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 樣板中顯示內嵌。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3aa1qnk9ya43ni9hn1jnhseyg\">應用程式將向瀏覽器渲染出房屋位置資料。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"conceptual-preview-of-interpolation\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4gc45ik6n2tghtdphqufffbxc\">內嵌的概念性預覽<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#conceptual-preview-of-interpolation\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9y3zcfy8jj3vhlcwozpgqxsv7\">在這一步中，你將使用內嵌在樣板中顯示值（屬性和\n<code>@Input</code>值）。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2n3m7rwvqcrkp3i8mqxa0s15i\">在 Angular 樣板中使用 <code>{{ expression }}</code>，可以從屬性、<code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 和有效的 JavaScript 表示式中渲染出值。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"asipuru2omgew95xvqgsfgj4a\">更深入的解釋，請參閱<a href=\"guide/interpolation\">使用內嵌顯示值</a>指南。</p>\n<h2 id=\"step-1---update-housinglocationcomponent-template-to-include-interpolated-values\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"161ln7nvaijk70b3oiyub574c\">第 1 步 - 更新 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 樣板以包含內嵌<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#step-1---update-housinglocationcomponent-template-to-include-interpolated-values\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"uxi21bo8ctmx019cv5phsbim\">此步驟在 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 樣板中新增新的 HTML 結構和內嵌。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eug3k0hymd4usfrh9oohvkiee\">在程式碼編輯器中：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2j1hhdzuzpzh4rxn5ms2fbmah\">導向到 <code>src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9299zvsz9fjqqoukf3956sbci\">在 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 裝飾器的 <code>template</code> 屬性中，將現有的 HTML 標記替換為以下程式碼：</p>\n<code-example header=\"Update HousingLocationComponent template\" path=\"first-app-lesson-07/src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts\" region=\"add-listing-details\">\ntemplate: `\n  &lt;section class=\"listing\"&gt;\n    &lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a> class=\"listing-photo\" [src]=\"housingLocation.photo\" alt=\"Exterior photo of {{housingLocation.name}}\"&gt;\n    &lt;h2 class=\"listing-heading\"&gt;{{ housingLocation.name }}&lt;/h2&gt;\n    &lt;p class=\"listing-location\"&gt;{{ housingLocation.city}}, {{housingLocation.state }}&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n  `,\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3v72239kh5mjoiuhk7cbmbuqm\">在此更新過的樣板程式碼中，你已使用屬性繫結將 <code>housingLocation.photo</code> 繫結到 <code>src</code> 屬性。而 <code>alt</code> 屬性透過內嵌為影象的替代文字提供更多上下文。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"37wqnxjirox9mw1ha2sr0hfsd\">你將使用內嵌來包含\n<code>housingLocation</code>屬性的\n<code>name</code>、\n<code>city</code>和\n<code>state</code>值。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"step-2---confirm-the-changes-render-in-the-browser\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8vkrmwq68zlqsmspiueye0fp6\">第 2 步 - 確認在瀏覽器中渲染出的更改<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#step-2---confirm-the-changes-render-in-the-browser\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7y9sibc49gz4j1owr3vr5a678\">儲存所有更改。</li>\n<li>Open the browser and confirm that the app renders the photo, city and state sample data.\n<section class=\"lightbox\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"45cg7u0871uzznwdk3vbaf5hs\"><img alt=\"browser frame of homes-app displaying logo, filter text input box, search button and the same housing location UI card\" src=\"generated/images/guide/faa/homes-app-lesson-07-step-2.png\" width=\"1629\" height=\"731\"></section>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"lesson-review\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckmo8mg671uh3oxv2z72tuj64\">課程回顧<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9kjxldi8tznsh8361o6f852z4\">在這節課中，你新增了一個新的 HTML 結構並使用 Angular 樣板語法在 <code>HousingLocation</code> 樣板中渲染出了值。現在，你有了兩個重要的技能：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2ewb06781tl7awanyv21pamsd\">將資料傳給元件</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"565sl7xfsprv96widdwsnemq\">將值插入樣板</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"825nzvudugny8gsg4z81zxs8h\">有了這些技能，應用程式現在就可以共享資料並在瀏覽器中顯示動態值。到目前為止這工作得很好。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vi4aou9du2w1ijyabax7x8qx\">如果你在學習這節課時遇到了任何問題，可以在<live-example></live-example>檢視完整程式碼。</p>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c4pkljueu68ifjoi5994e9l8o\">下一步<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b76pithxisprcv4e19xtbjl8q\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08\">第 8 課 - 使用 *ngFor 列出元件中的物件</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ep5mlw3d5q1ucm62jzem9a7pc\">有關這節課中涵蓋的主題的更多訊息，請訪問：<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c5n9o0xwd06vqprmuploo4agk\"><a href=\"/guide/interpolation\">顯示帶內嵌的值</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5o47inxztcg9bxn0itsl3sp23\"><a href=\"guide/template-syntax\">樣板語法</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Tue Jul 11 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /guide/interpolation\n - api/common/NgOptimizedImage\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Input\n - guide/interpolation\n - guide/template-syntax\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#conceptual-preview-of-interpolation\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#lesson-7---add-an-interpolation-to-a-components-template\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#lesson-review\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#next-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#step-1---update-housinglocationcomponent-template-to-include-interpolated-values\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#step-2---confirm-the-changes-render-in-the-browser\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07#what-youll-learn\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08\n-->"}